HEADWORD: Rolly-pooly
<hw>Roll"y-pool`y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Etymol.
uncertain.]</ety> <def>A game in which a ball, rolling into a certain
place, wins.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>rouly-pouly</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

